             was indicted for <rs id="t18200517-96-off562" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18200517-96-off562" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18200517-96-off562" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18200517-96-cd563" type="crimeDate">8th of May</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18200517-96-off562 t18200517-96-cd563"></join>, 50 lbs. of lead, value 5 s. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18200517-96-victim1018" type="victimName">
                           John 
                           Brice
                        <interp inst="t18200517-96-victim1018" type="surname" value="Brice"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18200517-96-victim1018" type="given" value="John"></interp>
